article.description: Vincent Eze tallied 16 points and 10 rebounds to lead Fairfield to a 66-54 win over Wagner on Saturday.
article.headline: Eze carries Fairfield past Wagner 66-54
article.story: NEW YORK -- Vincent Eze tallied 16 points and 10 rebounds to lead Fairfield to a 66-54 win over Wagner on Saturday. Landon Taliaferro had 17 points for Fairfield (4-7). Aidas Kavaliauskas added 10 points. Taj Benning had 10 points and six rebounds for the visiting team. Curtis Cobb III had 19 points for the Seahawks (3-8). Alex Morales added 11 points. Fairfield plays Niagara on the road on Friday. Wagner plays Mount St. Mary's on the road on Thursday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
